  "title": "TypeError: instantSearchInstance.sendEventToInsights is not a function",
  "body": "## 🐛 Bug description\r\n\r\nMy application started to throw exception: \r\n`TypeError: instantSearchInstance.sendEventToInsights is not a function` \r\n\r\nThe code is located inside `createSendEventForHits.js`\r\n\r\nI even upgraded to version `^4.8.3` but the problem is still happening. (using ` algoliasearch: ^4.5.1` and `vue-instantsearch 3.4.2`)\r\n\r\n## 🔍 Bug reproduction\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce the behavior:**\r\n\r\n1. Go to https://www.seek-team.com/en/players?country=FR,BE\r\n2. Click on \"Display player's map\"\r\n3. The error happens\r\n\r\n## 🖥 Screenshots\r\n\r\n![List_of_players_ready_to_join_your_esport_team_-_Search_your_future_gold_star_gamer_](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/346010/96931831-39bd9680-14be-11eb-996a-bd6ff7c2fa33.png)\r\n\r\n![List_of_players_ready_to_join_your_esport_team_-_Search_your_future_gold_star_gamer_](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/346010/96931678-f531fb00-14bd-11eb-9ad1-e62da997496f.png)\r\n",
